<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3817121>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Neobelocera biprocessa sp. nov., holotype (GUGC-FS-TN-20090401) A. Male habitus, dorsal view. B. Same, lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Same, lateral view. E. Face. F. Forewing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3817121/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3817125>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Neobelocera russa sp. nov., holotype (GUGC-FS-TN-20100801). A. Male habitus, dorsal view. B. Same, lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Same, lateral view. E. Face. F. Forewing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3817125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3817123>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Neobelocera biprocessa sp. nov., holotype (GUGC-FS-TN-20090401). A. Head and thorax, dorsal view. B. Face. C. Forewing. D. Male genitalia, posterior view. E. Same, lateral view. F. Pygofer, posterior view. G. Anal segment and aedeagus, lateral view. H. Genital style, posterior view. I. Same, lateral view. Scale bars: A–B, D–I = 0.2 mm; C = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3817123/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3817127>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Neobelocera russa sp. nov., holotype (GUGC-FS-TN-20100801). A. Head and thorax, dorsal view. B. Face. C. Forewing. D. Male genitalia, posterior view. E. Same, lateral view. F. Aedeagus, posterior view. G. Same, lateral view. H. Genital style, posterior view. I. Same, lateral view. Scale bars: A–B, D–I = 0.2 mm; C = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3817127/files/figure.png" ;
